text: Ernst Heinrich Landrock (4 August 1878 in Reinsdorf, Saxony - 30 April 1966 in Kreuzlingen, Switzerland) was a photographer who was based in Tunis, Leipzig and Cairo. He is known for his works with Rudolf Franz Lehnert, published as "Lehnert & Landrock". ==References== ==External links== * Lehnert & Landrock - Biography * original visuals used for the Muslimgauze's artworks, examples of photographs * Nooderlich photo festival Category:Photographers from Saxony Category:1878 births Category:1966 deaths Category:People from Zwickau (district)
